Changes for Perl extension Perl-Dist-Downloads

0.30 Mon 19 Nov 2007
	- Matching versions with Perl::Dist
	- Adding a three-set of bzlib2 packages
	- Adding a gmp package (Chris Williams)

0.04 Fri  9 Nov 2007
	- Adding a pexports package
	- Adding a zlib package
	- Adding an iconv package
	- Adding a libxml2 package
 
0.03 Mon 22 Oct 2007
	- Setting the guideline that Perl-Dist needs to work with a non-skip_perl
	  minicpan. Thus, removing perl-5.8.8.tar.gz because it will be available
	  in the minicpan.

0.02 Wed 17 Oct 2007
	- Adding the mingw runtime

0.01 Wed 17 Oct 2007
	- Creating initial version with dmake and several mingw packages
